  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Guatemala has a plastic pollution problem and Eco-Stores are the solution. Eco-Stores are the world&apos;s first stores where people can buy essential pantry items and household supplies in exchange for eco-bricks (empty plastic bottles filled with inorganic wastes) they produce themselves. This project motivates people to recycle plastics where recycling plastics is difficult. By supporting this project, you will help prevent plastic wastes from being burned or thrown into streets or rivers!</narrative>
  </description>
